+# ([K, N], TP_SPLIT_DIM)
+# Example:
+#  A shape of ([14336, 4096], 0) indicates the following GEMM shape,
+#   - TP1 : K = 14336, N = 4096
+#   - TP2 : K = 7168, N = 4096
